        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from mpl_toolkits.mplot3d import Axes3D\n",
        "\n",
        "class MobiusStrip:\n",
        "    def __init__(self, R, w, n):\n",
        "        self.R = R\n",
        "        self.w = w\n",
        "        self.n = n\n",
        "\n",
        "        self.u = np.linspace(0, 2 * np.pi, n)\n",
        "        self.v = np.linspace(-w / 2, w / 2, n)\n",
        "\n",
        "        self.x = None\n",
        "        self.y = None\n",
        "        self.z = None\n",
        "        self.surface_area = None\n",
        "        self.edge_length = None\n",
        "\n",
        "        self.create_surface()\n",
        "        self.calculate_surface_area()\n",
        "        self.calculate_edge_length()\n",
        "\n",
        "    def create_surface(self):\n",
        "        U, V = np.meshgrid(self.u, self.v)\n",
        "\n",
        "        self.x = (self.R + V * np.cos(U / 2)) * np.cos(U)\n",
        "        self.y = (self.R + V * np.cos(U / 2)) * np.sin(U)\n",
        "        self.z = V * np.sin(U / 2)\n",
        "\n",
        "    def calculate_surface_area(self):\n",
        "        du = 2 * np.pi / (self.n - 1)\n",
        "        dv = self.w / (self.n - 1)\n",
        "\n",
        "        total_area = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "        for i in range(self.n - 1):\n",
        "            for j in range(self.n - 1):\n",
        "                u = self.u[i]\n",
        "                v = self.v[j]\n",
        "\n",
        "                dx_du = -(self.R + v * np.cos(u / 2)) * np.sin(u) - v * 0.5 * np.sin(u / 2) * np.cos(u)\n",
        "                dy_du = (self.R + v * np.cos(u / 2)) * np.cos(u) - v * 0.5 * np.sin(u / 2) * np.sin(u)\n",
        "                dz_du = v * 0.5 * np.cos(u / 2)\n",
        "\n",
        "                dx_dv = np.cos(u / 2) * np.cos(u)\n",
        "                dy_dv = np.cos(u / 2) * np.sin(u)\n",
        "                dz_dv = np.sin(u / 2)\n",
        "\n",
        "                cross_x = dy_du * dz_dv - dz_du * dy_dv\n",
        "                cross_y = dz_du * dx_dv - dx_du * dz_dv\n",
        "                cross_z = dx_du * dy_dv - dy_du * dx_dv\n",
        "\n",
        "                magnitude = np.sqrt(cross_x**2 + cross_y**2 + cross_z**2)\n",
        "\n",
        "                total_area += magnitude * du * dv\n",
        "\n",
        "        self.surface_area = total_area\n",
        "\n",
        "    def calculate_edge_length(self):\n",
        "        edge1_points = []\n",
        "        edge2_points = []\n",
        "\n",
        "        for u in self.u:\n",
        "            v1 = self.w / 2\n",
        "            x1 = (self.R + v1 * np.cos(u / 2)) * np.cos(u)\n",
        "            y1 = (self.R + v1 * np.cos(u / 2)) * np.sin(u)\n",
        "            z1 = v1 * np.sin(u / 2)\n",
        "            edge1_points.append([x1, y1, z1])\n",
        "\n",
        "            v2 = -self.w / 2\n",
        "            x2 = (self.R + v2 * np.cos(u / 2)) * np.cos(u)\n",
        "            y2 = (self.R + v2 * np.cos(u / 2)) * np.sin(u)\n",
        "            z2 = v2 * np.sin(u / 2)\n",
        "            edge2_points.append([x2, y2, z2])\n",
        "\n",
        "        edge1_points = np.array(edge1_points)\n",
        "        edge2_points = np.array(edge2_points)\n",
        "\n",
        "        length1 = 0\n",
        "        length2 = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "        for i in range(len(edge1_points) - 1):\n",
        "            dist1 = np.sqrt(np.sum((edge1_points[i+1] - edge1_points[i])**2))\n",
        "            length1 += dist1\n",
        "\n",
        "            dist2 = np.sqrt(np.sum((edge2_points[i+1] - edge2_points[i])**2))\n",
        "            length2 += dist2\n",
        "\n",
        "        self.edge_length = length1 + length2\n",
        "\n",
        "    def plot(self):\n",
        "        fig = plt.figure()\n",
        "        ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')\n",
        "\n",
        "        ax.plot_surface(self.x, self.y, self.z)\n",
        "\n",
        "        ax.set_xlabel('X')\n",
        "        ax.set_ylabel('Y')\n",
        "        ax.set_zlabel('Z')\n",
        "        ax.set_title('Mobius Strip')\n",
        "\n",
        "        plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "    def show_properties(self):\n",
        "        print(f\"Radius: {self.R}\")\n",
        "        print(f\"Width: {self.w}\")\n",
        "        print(f\"Resolution: {self.n}\")\n",
        "        print(f\"Surface Area: {self.surface_area:.6f}\")\n",
        "        print(f\"Edge Length: {self.edge_length:.6f}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "def get_input():\n",
        "    while True:\n",
        "        try:\n",
        "            R = float(input(\"Radius R: \"))\n",
        "            if R <= 0:\n",
        "                print(\"Radius must be positive\")\n",
        "                continue\n",
        "\n",
        "            w = float(input(\"Width w: \"))\n",
        "            if w <= 0:\n",
        "                print(\"Width must be positive\")\n",
        "                continue\n",
        "\n",
        "            n = int(input(\"Resolution n: \"))\n",
        "            if n < 10:\n",
        "                print(\"Resolution must be at least 10\")\n",
        "                continue\n",
        "\n",
        "            return R, w, n\n",
        "\n",
        "        except ValueError:\n",
        "            print(\"Enter valid numbers\")\n",
        "        except KeyboardInterrupt:\n",
        "            return None, None, None\n",
        "\n",
        "if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n",
        "    R, w, n = get_input()\n",
        "\n",
        "    if R is None:\n",
        "        exit()\n",
        "\n",
        "    mobius = MobiusStrip(R, w, n)\n",
        "    mobius.show_properties()\n",
        "    mobius.plot()"
      ]
    }
